## Documentation

Install:

```bash
pip install packaging-version-git
```

Usage:

```python
from packaging_version_git import GitVersion

version = GitVersion.from_tag()
print(version) # 0.1.0

version = GitVersion.from_commit(as_dev=True)
print(version) # 0.1.0.dev5+ef7fd31
```

